%% OpenVINO Model Server - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as OpenShift Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OVMS as OVMS Container<br/>gRPC/REST (configurable)
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime<br/>(in-process)
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,OVMS: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (RHOAI 3.x)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Gateway->>RBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS
        RBAC->>RBAC: RBAC authorization check
        RBAC->>OVMS: Forward to OVMS<br/>HTTP or gRPC (plaintext)<br/>localhost
        OVMS->>OV: Execute inference<br/>C++ API (in-process)
        OV-->>OVMS: Inference result
        OVMS-->>RBAC: Response
        RBAC-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over OVMS,Storage: Flow 2: Model Loading from Remote Storage
        OVMS->>Storage: Download model files<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials
        Storage-->>OVMS: Model artifacts
        OVMS->>OV: Load model into runtime<br/>C++ API (in-process)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over OVMS,HF: Flow 3: HuggingFace Model Pull
        OVMS->>HF: GET model files<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (optional)
        HF-->>OVMS: Model files + config
        OVMS->>OVMS: Optional: optimum-cli conversion<br/>Python subprocess
        OVMS->>OV: Load converted model
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over Client,OV: Flow 4: LLM Streaming (OpenAI-compatible)
        Client->>OVMS: POST /v3/v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP (stream=true)
        OVMS->>OV: MediaPipe LLM Calculator<br/>ContinuousBatching
        loop Token Generation
            OV-->>OVMS: Generated token
            OVMS-->>Client: SSE data chunk<br/>HTTP chunked/SSE
        end
        OVMS-->>Client: SSE [DONE]
    end
